@startuml
title Horizon Bank process-architecture decomposition and traceability

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #334155
skinparam ArrowFontColor #1E293B
skinparam ArrowFontSize 11
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
  RoundCorner 8
}

rectangle "CATALOGUE LEVEL\nCustomer and party management\nProcess family" as FAMILY #E0F2FE
rectangle "END-TO-END LEVEL\nEstablish customer relationship\nProcess" as PROCESS #DBEAFE

package "SELECTED SUBPROCESS LEVEL" #FFFFFF {
  rectangle "Capture\napplication" as CAPTURE
  rectangle "Verify identity\nand screen" as VERIFY
  rectangle "Resolve\nreferral" as REFERRAL #FEF3C7
  rectangle "Create party and\naccount records" as CREATE
  rectangle "Confirm usable\nservice" as CONFIRM
  CAPTURE -[hidden]right- VERIFY
  VERIFY -[hidden]right- REFERRAL
  REFERRAL -[hidden]right- CREATE
  CREATE -[hidden]right- CONFIRM
}

rectangle "OUTCOME\nUsable banking relationship" as OUTCOME #DCFCE7
rectangle "ACCOUNTABILITY\nOnboarding process owner" as OWNER #F3E8FF
rectangle "CONTROLS\nIdentity evidence\nScreening evidence" as CONTROLS #FEE2E2
rectangle "MEASURES\nElapsed time | Straight-through processing\nReferral rate | Control failures" as MEASURES #FEF3C7
rectangle "CAPABILITIES EXERCISED\nCustomer Onboarding | Identity Verification\nFinancial Crime Screening | Party Management | Account Opening" as CAPS #E0E7FF
rectangle "REFERENCE RESPONSIBILITIES\nCandidate BIAN Service Domains and interactions\nBIAN 14.0 logical reference\nCandidate, partial and many-to-many" as BIAN #F1F5F9
rectangle "SELECTED DETAIL\nBPMN collaboration for behaviour\nand referral exception\nNot a full-bank process diagram" as BPMN #ECFDF5

FAMILY -down-> PROCESS : contains
PROCESS -down-> CAPTURE : decomposes to
PROCESS -down-> VERIFY : decomposes to
PROCESS -down-> REFERRAL : decomposes to
PROCESS -down-> CREATE : decomposes to
PROCESS -down-> CONFIRM : decomposes to

OWNER -[hidden]down- OUTCOME
OUTCOME -[hidden]down- CONTROLS
CONTROLS -[hidden]down- MEASURES
MEASURES -[hidden]down- CAPS
CAPS -[hidden]down- BIAN
BIAN -[hidden]down- BPMN

PROCESS -right-> OWNER : accountable role
PROCESS -right-> OUTCOME : produces
PROCESS -right-> CONTROLS : is constrained by
PROCESS -right-> MEASURES : is measured by
PROCESS -right-> CAPS : exercises
PROCESS -right-> BIAN : is informed by
PROCESS -right-> BPMN : details selected behaviour

note bottom
  Selected Horizon Bank onboarding excerpt.
  Process, capability, BIAN responsibility and implementation are not equivalent.
end note
@enduml
